        Add test_sha512_vectors() to results
        
        Note: Test SHA-3 family
        Add test_sha3_256_basic() to results
        Add test_sha3_384_basic() to results
        Add test_sha3_512_basic() to results
        
        Note: Test BLAKE2 variants
        Add test_blake2b_basic() to results
        Add test_blake2s_basic() to results
        
        Note: Test HMAC functionality
        Add test_hmac_sha256() to results
