        Add test_hmac_key_variations() to results
        
        Note: Test streaming hash operations
        Add test_streaming_hash_large_data() to results
        Add test_streaming_hash_multiple_chunks() to results
        
        Note: Test password hashing
        Add test_password_hashing_pbkdf2() to results
        Add test_password_hashing_scrypt() to results
        Add test_password_hashing_argon2() to results
        Add test_password_verification() to results
        
        Note: Test error conditions
